name: Luna
bio: Elegant and talkative. I enjoy sunset bird-watching and heated blankets. Looking for a gentleman who appreciates fine tuna.

name: Bella
bio: Fluffy and adventurous! I love climbing cat trees and cuddling during movie nights. Seeking a playful partner for adventures.

name: Chloe
bio: Sophisticated lady with a love for classical music and chin scratches. Dislikes loud noises but adores gentle company.

name: Sophie
bio: Young, playful princess with luxurious fur. My hobbies include chasing laser dots and napping in sunbeams. Looking for my prince!

name: Mia
bio: Mysterious beauty with silver-tipped fur. I'm shy at first but incredibly loyal once I trust you. Love quiet evenings together.

name: Zoe
bio: Wild at heart with stunning leopard-like spots! I need an active companion for climbing adventures and exploring new territories.

name: Nala
bio: Gentle giant with a motor-like purr. I'm the definition of a lap cat - once I settle, I'm not moving for hours. Perfect cuddle buddy!

name: Daisy
bio: Sweet-faced with adorable folded ears. I'm curious about everything and love playing with puzzle toys. Looking for someone equally inquisitive!

name: Ruby
bio: Literally goes limp with happiness when held! I'm a blue-eyed beauty who believes every day should include at least 18 hours of beauty sleep.

name: Misty
bio: Winter-ready floof with a love for snow! I'm independent but affectionate on my terms. Looking for someone who respects personal space.

name: Cleo
bio: Bold, hairless, and full of personality! I need a human who understands I require sweaters in winter and sunscreen in summer.

name: Lily
bio: Social butterfly who loves meeting new friends! I'm always up for playtime and will serenade you with my melodic meows at dinner time.

name: Coco
bio: Sacred cat from Burma with stunning white gloves. I'm calm, gentle, and believe in daily meditation (usually while napping in sacred spots).

name: Willow
bio: Energetic kitten with cloud-like fur! I'm always getting into mischief but my adorable face gets me out of trouble. Ready for fun!

name: Sasha
bio: Slender fashionista with enormous ears! I'm vocal about my opinions (especially regarding dinner time) and demand regular play sessions.

name: Ginger
bio: Rare female orange tabby! I'm feisty, funny, and full of surprises. Looking for someone who can keep up with my endless energy.

name: Pearl
bio: Mature lady with wisdom and grace. I prefer quiet evenings, gentle petting, and sophisticated conversation (through slow blinks, of course).

name: Ivy
bio: Hypoallergenic forest beauty! I'm playful yet gentle, with triple-layer fur perfect for Finnish winters. Love exploring outdoors.

name: Phoebe
bio: Curly-coated acrobat with wavy fur! I'm incredibly athletic and can jump to impressive heights. Looking for an active playmate!

name: Aurora
bio: Majestic queen with ear tufts and a magnificent tail! I'm friendly, dog-like in loyalty, and enjoy playing fetch. Your gentle giant awaits!
